ffmpeg-the-third
----------------

URL:     https://github.com/shssoichiro/ffmpeg-the-third
License: WTFPL (Do What The Fuck You Want To Public License)

ffmpeg-the-third is a Rust binding for FFmpeg, used by analog-felx for
video decode, encode, and probing. It is a fork of the rust-ffmpeg crate
that tracks recent FFmpeg upstream more aggressively.

FFmpeg
------

URL:     https://ffmpeg.org/
License: LGPL-2.1+ (the build configuration we link against, with `--enable-gpl`
         not specified). Some optional libraries used by FFmpeg are GPL-2+;
         we ship LGPL-only builds in our installers.

analog-felx links to FFmpeg's libraries (libavcodec, libavformat,
libavutil, libavfilter, libswscale, libswresample) at runtime. The
installer for each platform bundles those shared libraries; users may
also use a system-installed FFmpeg.

